# Job Position Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create job position (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/job-positions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Backend Developer",
  "recruitmentPlanId": "<plan-id>",
  "description": "Develop and maintain APIs",
  "requirements": "Node.js, NestJS",
  "targetCount": 5
}

### Get all job positions (public)
GET http://localhost:3001/job-positions

### Get job position by ID (public)
GET http://localhost:3001/job-positions/{{id}}

### Update job position (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/job-positions/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Senior Backend Developer"
}

### Delete job position (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/job-positions/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
